text.tspan: $2080 is the token that acts as the pillar of DUST80. $2080 aims to establish a sustainable
in-game currency that stabilizes the entire ecosystem.
The reward pool is mainly focused on crediting three categories of players:
Dedicated players
Ecosystem contributors
Risk-takers
We aim for our token value to have a strong correlation with user count and activity.
$2080 TOKEN
We believe in providing a distinguished value proposition to players
The current status quo model for P2E-tokenomics is problematic because non-contributors
and bots acquire tokens and cause inflation. Our tokenomics is based on a tier system,
where true contributors to the game economy will get far more credit.
A number of in-game activities will be needed to acquire certain resources in-game, where
you need to train yourself to become more skillful.
We make ecosystems that are enjoyable. DUST80 is designed to thrive on the value of the
growth of our game.
We build games and NFT eco-system that is enjoyable. NO MORE, NO LESS.
Value Proposition
We believe that only a great game has longevity. You play it because you love it, and in
return, you get rewarded. This is a distinction from most P2E games, where great
gameplay is secondary to earning tokens. For this cause, we built sustainable
tokenomics.
We believe in making an eco-system where the players should put money and token to
get the value of “fun” gameplay.

You are your Harrier - welcome to the battlefield. Attack other factions, or
defend your own base. Support your soldiers by giving orders and deploying
special attacks during battle to support them.
Build your outpost, and maintain your defenses system against
attackers by deploying and upgrading your base. The gameplay will go on even
when you are away, and the defense results will be rewarded according to the
outcome of events during this time.
Upgrade and specialize your army to fight against others. Win the fight
and plunder your enemy base. Send your Harriers by recruiting new people to
your troops.
The game features asynchronous multiplayer combat where attackers
compete against other players' defensive bases. Watch replays of your opponent's
attacks and perform successful reprisals to earn bonus loot and resources.
The game contains a system to test your guts. If you would like to have
more benefits, you gotta be ready to put your resources on the line. The more you
bet, the bigger the win.
Play against holders of other projects together with your
friends and earn tokens. Reach the top of the leaderboards. Holders of DUST80
will enjoy the best interactive gameplay experience.

Battle Field
Wars have always been a part of the modern human, even in the
post-apocalyptic wasteland of DUST80. We must live through
and overcome this tragic reality, fight for our lives by defeating
the enemy, and move on with our lives.
Engine Houston is the first project to be pursued in our IP. With
your NFT as your identity and symbol of Township, we invite
you to a Free-to-play game where you can earn tokens for your
accomplishments. This one game will never represent the entire
IP project of DUST80, but we don't plan on making a game that
isn't perfect either.
